===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun}}

# {{often|in plural}} The [[sky]].
# {{context|theology}} The [[paradise]] of the [[afterlife]] in certain [[religion]]s, considered to be the home of the [[god]] or gods of those religions.
#: ''Mommy’s gone to '''heaven''' to be with God.''
# {{italbrac|used without the article}} A [[blissful]] place or experience.
#: ''Soaking in a warm bath after a long day at work is sheer heaven.''

